txt.en: Defeat Morgul Captains in Rath Dúath ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
Strong Orcs can be found in Rath Dúath.\n\nYou should defeat Morgul Captains and warg-masters.
A bounty notice asks you to hunt down prominent Orcs in Rath Dúath.
You defeated some of the stronger, more high-ranking Orcs in Rath Dúath. The disarray should prove useful to those who find themselves tasked with cleansing evil from the valley.

The bounty notice reads:

'We need someone to do something about the Orcs. Not just the rank-and-file warriors, though. We need you to defeat the leaders, the intelligent Orcs that give out the orders to all the rest. Those are the ones that have the potential to cause us the most grief.

'There's a reward in it for you if you can slay some of the higher-ranking Orcs: Morgul Captains and warg-masters.'
Defeat Morgul warg-masters in Rath Dúath ([placeholder]/[placeholder])
